'''荣誉学位'''在不同学位和教育制度的背景下具有多种含义。最常见的是，它指的是[[本科教育|本科]][[學士|学士学位]]的一种。本科学士荣誉学位通常包含拥有有更高的学术水平。有别于普通的学士学位。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Ivey HBA Program Brochure|url=https://online.flippingbook.com/view/439134/?sharedOn=|accessdate=2021-03-12|date=2020|work=|publisher=[[Ivey_Business_School|Ivey Business School]] at the [[University_of_Western_Ontario|University of Western Ontario]]|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414234511/https://online.flippingbook.com/view/439134/?sharedOn=|dead-url=no}}</ref>

荣誉学位有时会在学位缩写后用“ Hons ”标注。各地标注方式会有所不同，例如“"BA (Hons)", "B.A., Hons"等等。在加拿大，荣誉学位可以在学位缩写之前用“ H”表示，例如"荣誉商业管理学士"会简写为“ HBA”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Undergraduate Programs: Bachelor of Arts degree|url=https://uwaterloo.ca/future-students/programs/bachelor-of-arts|accessdate=2021-03-12|date=2019-06-27|work=[[University_of_Waterloo|University of Waterloo]]|language=en|quote=What is the abbreviation for an honours Bachelor of Arts? The common abbreviations are BA or HBA.|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102213457/https://uwaterloo.ca/future-students/programs/bachelor-of-arts|dead-url=no}}</ref>

